Lanius excubitor excubitor Linnaeus, 1758
Lanius excubitor funereus Menzbier, 1894
Lanius excubitor homeyeri Cabanis, 1873
Lanius excubitor mollis Eversmann, 1853
Lanius excubitor sibiricus (Bogdanov, 1881)


